<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema611_10_su_0007_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema611_10.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema611_10_su_0007">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-type="1" data-text="자기주도 3">
          <span class="blue line" lang="y">내 힘으로 풀어요</span>
          <span lang="y">공부한 내용을 확인해요</span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="title type2 jgjd_3_sub_title">
        <h2 data-head="6" lang="y" class="is_star fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              철사
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>8</span>
                <span>9</span>
              </div>
              &nbsp;m를 겹치지 않게 모두 사용하여 크기가 같은 정삼각형 2개를 만들었습니다. 만든 정삼각형의 한 변의 길이는 몇 m인지
            </div>
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              구하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.
            </div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">정삼각형 한 개를 만드는 데 사용한 철사의 길이는 몇 m인지 구해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="contents_inwrap">
            <div class="equation_box">
              <div class="title" lang="y">식</div>
  
              <div class="input_area">
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(8)/(9)-:2" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span>=</span>
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(4)/(9)" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
  
            <div class="answer_box">
              <div class="title" lang="y">답</div>
  
              <div class="input_area">
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(4)/(9)" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span>m</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">만든 정삼각형의 한 변의 길이는 몇 m인지 구해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="contents_inwrap">
            <div class="equation_box">
              <div class="title" lang="y">식</div>
  
              <div class="input_area">
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(4)/(9)-:3" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span>=</span>
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(4)/(27)" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
  
            <div class="answer_box">
              <div class="title" lang="y">답</div>
  
              <div class="input_area">
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(4)/(27)" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span>m</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
